description.en:
Alex has a lot of respect and admiration for his cousin Diwa. This is because he is his guardian while he is studying in Manila.

During Alex's temporary work at the library as an OJT, he met librarian Yal Ogana.

His Kuya Diwa is strict but kind.

Yal is stern and rude.

While Alex is with his Kuya Diwa and Yal, he can't help but notice that there is something strange between the two. It's as if they are not just friends. It seems like the two are just hiding their true feelings for each other.
